{"tid":204074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"12歲童涉強姦3歲女","createTime":"2017-04-16T17:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T04:20:17.000Z","uid":82394,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a844988ac01c54f04ecc51f453804da74d55c16f","tid":204074,"uid":82394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T17:34:22.000Z","msg":"印度北方邦一名12歲男童涉嫌誘姦3歲女童，多名鄰居聽到女童尖叫聲後趕至，不禁被眼前一幕嚇呆。<br />\n<br />\n事發在上周六，涉案男童用牛油奶做餌，成功從女童家中將她誘拐。當地警方表示，由於兩家人及男女童本身相識，故男童將女童帶走時，鄰居們都無起疑心。男童將女童帶回家後露出狼相，女童哭叫起來，慘叫聲驚動鄰居，多名鄰居上門了解情況，被現場情況嚇呆，他們將男童捉住並報警，又安排女童送院接受治療。<br />\n<br />\n警方指涉案男童父母都是工人，可能無瑕管教，男童終日遊手好閒，案發時也只有他一人在家。警方表示：「由於他是未成年兒童，故我們不能過度盤問他。他也許是學壞了。」警方已將男童投進監獄。<br />\n<br />\n印度時報  <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170413/19989283\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170413%2F19989283&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLuwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=44dbb651\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170413%2F19989283&h=1a32a12b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170413/19989283</a>"},{"pid":"62cb0f8261428060a98df5e21af68aa003aa2df7","tid":204074,"uid":15620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T17:36:53.000Z","msg":"...."},{"pid":"468927108ae359506c7599c0572886e821fc85b4","tid":204074,"uid":5822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T17:37:40.000Z","msg":"估中國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a931724ce4292c1928aea5ce8eb3f012c09fd5","tid":204074,"uid":97104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T17:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shock